# Fretwire

```elixir
Mix.install(
  [
    {:kino, "~> 0.18.0"},
    {:fretwire, path: Path.join([__DIR__, "fretwire"]), env: :dev}
  ],
  config_path: :fretwire,
  lockfile: :fretwire
)
```

